Resource Profile: ProfileSubstanceDefinitionForSubstanceSpecification

Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/5.0/StructureDefinition/profile-SubstanceDefinition-for-SubstanceSpecification Version: 0.0.1-snapshot-3
Standards status: Trial-use Active as of 2026-02-21 Maturity Level: 0 Computable Name: ProfileSubstanceDefinitionForSubstanceSpecification

This cross-version profile allows R5 SubstanceDefinition content to be represented via FHIR R4 SubstanceSpecification resources.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Cross-version Extension `R5.ActivityDefinition.product[x]` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.ActivityDefinition.subject[x]` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.ClinicalUseDefinition` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.Ingredient` for use in FHIR R4... Show 7 more, Cross-version Extension `R5.MedicinalProductDefinition.impurity` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.PlanDefinition.subject[x]` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.ResearchStudy.focus` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.SpecimenDefinition.typeTested.container.additive` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.Substance.code` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.SubstanceDefinition.relationship.substanceDefinition[x]` for use in FHIR R4 and Cross-version Extension `R5.ClinicalUseDefinition.contraindication.otherTherapy` for use in FHIR R4

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
